{"tid":815211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人口嚴重過盛還硬要輸入人口，政府你想迫我去邊？","createTime":"2018-09-12T00:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T13:47:51.000Z","uid":197219,"like":193,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"8320153d10cd69fce374b5da0c4929447e95d66f","tid":815211,"uid":197219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T00:59:24.000Z","msg":"無論你政治取向係邊一方，<br />\n人口過盛都係一個不爭既事實<br />\n<br />\n我地平時返工放工或者出街都已經多人到傻<br />\n<br />\n資源分配更加係一個解決唔到既問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我其實仲後生，<br />\n但移民愈來愈難既情況之下，<br />\n好多人只可以繼續係香港受苦<br />\n<br />\n你班仆街仲係咁輸入人口，<br />\n自己就拿外國passport<br />\n政府你究竟想迫我地去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS我都知你班仆街想人口大換血趕我地返大陸"},{"pid":"53b224f3f23b9619117a6b822b69f93b90a69bac","tid":815211,"uid":108347,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:01:57.000Z","msg":"如果佢地會諗你，佢地就唔係仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好ff埋啲不切實際嘅嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573bc0baed2c088fedcf84cd5089e03f757f3512","tid":815211,"uid":132038,"like":20,"dislike":4,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:03:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4a89006d4f0b3a88ea70005bc50b4d59e7fda70a","tid":815211,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:03:29.000Z","msg":"大灣區"},{"pid":"35c3792fa4db6738c6cb332d071372c9e4ebc51e","tid":815211,"uid":130051,"like":38,"dislike":6,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:05:06.000Z","msg":"我就拎外國passport既，但係會留守到香港滅亡果日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 始終香港先係我地屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73eb3274edd4ef24e34008c9204973f8c3a14e17","tid":815211,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:05:15.000Z","msg":"要團聚，躝上大灣區"},{"pid":"94ccbc3f7050caae61c659bdcefaa5b80fdc5fac","tid":815211,"uid":197219,"like":16,"dislike":1,