精神狀況亦都開始有問題，諗緊resign然後離開香港一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而個死老野高血壓，我好開心，抵撚死<br />\n睇下幾時激死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a9068d5285f78e6275d38b799b0f5db0ac580d28","tid":815211,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:49:10.000Z","msg":"賣女就聽得多<br />\n養埋個女婿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addd838d4c96c21745b9c01df0ec0496e29e349f","tid":815211,"uid":183178,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:49:20.000Z","msg":"人口係咪嚴重過剩唔夠膽落定論，因為世界頭三位人口密度最高既地方無香港份<br />\n<br />\n而香港就有最高既樓價，所以我覺得係土地政策問題"},{"pid":"5c9e7a61328ec0adccadcf08aca00775ac407103","tid":815211,"uid":14103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:50:32.000Z","msg":"迫我地去死囉 我地心有反共心 將來話唔定修例 唔愛國要坐監"},{"pid":"5b0932360e0ec04ac912ff87f14f4189e020b90b","tid":815211,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:51:26.000Z","msg":"逼你幫手拎枝槍屠殺呀<br />\n屌你"},{"pid":"32c2e32feb52181d412fc9479103767efe5cff85","tid":815211,"uid":163302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"addd838d4c96c21745b9c01df0ec0496e29e349f","tid":815211,"uid":183178,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:49:20.000Z","msg":"人口係咪嚴重過剩唔夠膽落定論，因為世界頭三位人口密度最高既地方無香港份<br />\n<br />\n而香港就有最高既樓價，所以我覺得係土地政策問題"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T01:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港係因為山多，可直接發展空間少，你試下打開地圖比較澳門（三甲有份）同香港山地同平原比例先啦"},{"pid":"63be125148e782043b948921b534751641dcc5b1","tid":815211,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"q